---
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy and Safety">
  <Container>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl py-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-teal-700">
        Wahkonsa Lodge
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
        Privacy and Safety
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700">
        <p>
          Wahkonsa Lodge is intended to be friendly, creative, and
          school-friendly. Children, parents, and teachers may use the coloring
          page request form to suggest ideas for future printable coloring pages.
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
            What We Ask For
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            The request form asks for a requester type, coloring page idea,
            purpose, optional grade or age range, optional style preferences, and
            an optional email address. Email is not required.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
            What Not to Include
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Please do not include private information such as a full name, school
            name, address, phone number, location, or anything that identifies a
            child. If you are under 13, please have a parent or teacher help you
            submit a request.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
            How Requests Are Used
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Requests are sent by email to Wahkonsa Lodge for review. Selected
            ideas may be edited, combined, skipped, or turned into printable
            coloring pages. We do not publish requester email addresses.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Spam Protection
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            The request form uses basic spam protection, including a hidden
            honeypot field, rate limiting, and Cloudflare Turnstile. Technical
            details such as user agent and IP address may be included in the
            request email to help reduce abuse.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Questions
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you have questions about a request, use the optional email field
            on the form or contact Wahkonsa Lodge through the site.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </Container>
</Layout>
